@host = http://localhost:5009

### Register customer
POST {{host}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Version: 1.0

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com"
}

###

### Get customer by ID (replace with a real ID)
GET {{host}}/api/customers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Api-Version: 1.0

###

### Health — liveness
GET {{host}}/health

###

### Health — readiness
GET {{host}}/health/ready

###
